GOODNESS..the things that go on in my life....~

MAN! i feel real good right now! i have no idea why...well actually there is a reason~ i had a good critique in photo workshop~ hehehe jimmy was truly honest and i'm glad he encouraged me!! hehehe yea i've been having a BAD week and that made me feel good~ but yea it was great what rod and jimmy said~ and even though ppl in the class weren't listening i was and i'm glad that they brought me up from the slumps of the week~ 

well, i'm soo tired today and i wished that i could go to sleep tho i REALLY want to go out somewhere! it is so sad that im here typing on lj on friday night~ well, im going out~ cya ^.^;

it's saturday and i have nothing to do, but update...such a sad life~ lol no but i am still happy~ a little silence is a good thing! hehehe i love it~ well, nothing has happened but i've been becoming more comfortable with this new york scene~ and school is great~ tho i failed my midterm...and when i say failed then that means i got a B....it's so sad that i got lower than an A on a open note test...oh well life goes on!

anyways, 
janine~ have a good trip back and get better!! THERA FLU!!! hehehe
V~ have fun at home~ enjoy it and come back happy~~
masako~ CALL ME!!! NOWWWW!!! lol~
everyone else~ have a good weekend!!! ^.^

on break right now~ kinda bored and hungry~ wished that someone would eat with me.. well can't get everything in life~ lol but yea class was ok i guess and i got an excellent on my essay i turned in last week and of course this midterm was crazy! i checked over all the questions like 10 times~ and i still got some wrong cause people got different answers than me! ahh well, i need to get an A so that i can stay here for 4 years....man i need a 4.0~ and i can do it~ but if i keep slacking im never going to get there~~ ahh well whatever i will do well...hehehe don't you love how i argue with myself~ haha

anyways..i'm still happy~ like my icon~ lol yea ...it's cause of how people have been treating me~ and if you have to ask who it might be then you don't know~

ok well i've been so busy these days! i feel like multiple things are pulling at me in different directions..but you know it's all good cause God is good and that's all that matters...hehehee 

well, i haven't been seeing many ppl these days and i apologize for that but it's been hectic~ and even on days off i feel like there's so much stuff to do~ but i enjoy it~

i'm so happy with my life right now~ and i truly believe God has provided and has given me this life~ i feel so good! hehee man i have never felt this way and i feel like floating~ hehe it's great! anyways i will end with~ a good night and a God bless~ =)

HAPPY BIRTHDAY ANGIE!!!!!!!!!!!!! BIG 18!!! yay~~~~~~ for those of you that didn't know! SHAME ON YOU!! lol~~~~~~ anyways be nice to her!!!

anyways! GOOD WEEKEND! good retreat! and good people!!!! lots of cool people! yay!!! made some GOOD friends and gave 4 guys a back massages.....lol don't take the wrong idea! haha~ but yea it was great...i got NO SLEEP~ but it's all good~ it was bonding time! =) hehee~

MIDTERMS!!! ARE THIS WEEK! omg pray for me~~~~~ hehee

OMG so happy today also.. hopefully sarah knows by now...lol hehehe but yea the ppl that know why im happy...well be happy for me...and don't bring me down...lol cause some ppl have (not naming ppl) but yea i'm still happy~~~ it's 3:21am and i have class in like 8hrs....that's great!...NOT but yea need to sleep~

TODAY was exhausting....and i wish it would end better on other weeks...also! i have sooo much to do this week! 3 midterms and a video project!! ahhh i'm so screwed! and i have to read a book and go find one in the library! ahh soo much! and on top of that i have to go find a job!! omgomgomgomgomgomgomgomgomgomgomgomg.... well hopefully at starbucks....??? devra come with me!! it's the 21st of OCT!! alright! lol

anyways nite guys...

if you're confused about the first part....then you have no business knowing! =P hehee

wow~ tonight was special~ im happy~ if you don't understand then you don't understand hehee~~~ ^.^; hopefully there will be more of those times~~

well can't wait till the retreat and the weekend~ OMG i went to vidal sassoon (sp?) and i got my hair looked at and they told me to come back friday for the final casting cut for hair design. i hope they pic me!! it's $200.00 for them to play with your hair on a stage! it's great!!! hahaha well connie and i are gonna go back on friday and hopefully they will pick us! hehehee

have class all day tomorrow~ not really looking forward to it and did i say that my ESSAY SUCKS...oh well i have to deal with it~ =P

SOMEONE HELP ME~ MY HEAD IS FILLED WITH SOO MUCH AND I WISH I COULD CONCENTRATE!!!! =(

another update...and it seems like no one reads it...cause ppl ask me how ny is...read my lj and you will know~ goodness...anyways i had a photo shoot today in the studio! it was so exciting...hehhee took pics of masako and myself in wierd expressions..haha it can't wait to print it~ THANX MASAKO! hehee

well, met some new ppl yesterday and had dinner with them and just got back from talking to some other ppl~ hehee i love it here~ meeting ppl left and right~ OMG and i found another danny oppa here! haha he looks exactly like him and even talks like him...well sometimes..haha well can't wait till the weeks over...so that i can meet up with other ppl~ well that's all for now~ nite

i went to the met today...for class and guess wut! the teacher didn't show up and so the class was standing there for like 25 min. after 11:00am and we went to go ask the ppl there if there was a reservation for our class so we asked and apparently the teacher was supposed to check in at 10:30am...and she didn't at all...so they gave us our little pins...they were blue! soo cute...anyways we went up to the daguerreotype exhibit and it was pretty cool~ it's nice to see early processed photography~~~but we all picked one favorite picture wrote it down and took a paper and left...of course being at the met~ i HAD to go see MONET! yea he's the best! i love his work!!! i like had to go to his section and absorb the artisticness...haha

but i stod in front of the japanese bridge painting for like 5 min, just looking at his detail. i've seen that painting soo many times and every time i love it even more than the last! yes..i am obsessed! hehehehee

well, then we left and tara went her own way and katie and i took the 6 to 23rd...came back and ate lunch...i kind of want to go to church tonight..but it's too late...oh well, going to have my own little session...hehehehee~~~ 

SUSHI NIGHT IN THE SOLARIUM! hehehe COME!

today was an interesting day...hmm well, my first class ended at 10 and i had all this free time so i went to the library and printed some stuff...then took the PE...it was ok i guess..i wrote about sexual conduct...yea it was interesting..hope i passed!

well went to pick a bagel and got a panini~ it was sooo good! i have to stop spending money! anyways after that i had some time to myself...it was nice!

well then went to class but before then i went to the kccc meeting..just to stop by cause sonya wanted me to. and GUESS WUT! she got me a cake and a present! I WAS SO SURPRISED! OMG i wish that i could eat the cake but i had to get to class~ i felt so loved! omg i've only known her for like a week and a half and she did all that for me! i was so surprised! Sonya if you read this THANK YOU SOO MUCH! 

anyways that made my day! hehee well, class was BORING i'm so glad the 5 weeks are up so now i don't have to see that teacher ever again! muhahahaa...hehe can't wait till tomorrow~ i get to make prints of janine and lauryn~ THANX GUYS FOR MODELING FOR ME!!! hehee ^.^;

oh yea by the way im not going home...i have a class this sunday and it's in place of the one on monday..SO MONDAY OFF YAY!!!

ok this is going to sound really stupid but i'm goin home..this weekend....and now after 2 hrs going by...i kind of don't want to....

ahh i know im crazy but i realized that there is nothing to do down there in MD..that's y i left it! ahhh man i don't want to go....hmm maybe i shouldn't...well help me out! leave a comment and tell me if i should go...i dunno... i want to but now it's like...i'll get there and there will be no one to hang with! so why go! ahh i dunno! HELP! =(

anyways going to sleep~ nite~~

well...where do i start....went to chiptole with masako and it was def better than the other burrito i had! it didn't pop! lol 

well, it's kind of sad today~ i realize my bday is coming and my friends aren't coming up and so i have no one to celebrate my past 18 years with...=( so sad...i know i have friends up here but it's different and all that you are reading this, I KNOW YOU UNDERSTAND WHAT I MEAN so don't get offended~ ^.^; well, i wish angie could come up~ it would be fun and we could catch up on old times....well that can be for another day~

THIS SECTION IS TO THOSE WHO RESPECT ME BEING A CHRISTIAN~

i realized that school and making new friends is important but after setting things straight and setting my priorities...i have come to realize that i need to do things not for myself but for God...there are so many things going on up here an i have been not a very good christian~ i need to get myself back on track and need not focus on Him and not on myself~ God should be the center and i haven't been a good child...so i confess that Jesus is Lord over all and i love Him with all my heart and soul. =)

good day today...rents came up and they were good to me...haha..it's kinda crazy..that i kind of miss them....my brother looks...."different" he needs to get a hair cut...haha 

anyways ate a lot in k-town and i got sooo much stuff from my parents! i have soo much of these little snacks...haha i'm going to gain soo much weight! ahh i can't!! haha 

so went to the freedom fellowship meeting and it was awesome! like ususal any type of fellowship with fellow Christians is awesome! haha well the bible study was good and listening to daniel share the gospel was awesome~ yea i like the word awesome...don't make fun of me...hehehe anyways~ it was great and i was going to go out to eat with them...but it's what? 11:00pm? and i just got back...haha i can't eat that late...

well also....i can't wait till church tomorrow~ janine is coming with me!!! yay!!

well, i went to gethsemane prayer metting and i met a cool bunch of ppl! from sva~~ haha it was great and all of them are so friendly...prollie cause they want me to go to their meetings...haha which i can't go to cause i have class....well anyways~ the walk back was soooooo scary!!!!!!!OMG there was soo many "sketchy" ppl on the street at midnight! ahhh soo FREAKY!!! i was like praying the whole time and beacuse of God i got through this whole walk~ OMG SOOO SCARY! and random ppl will say stuff and look at me and they were INVADING PERSONAL SPACE....thank God i had a hoodie sweater on...that way i could pretend i was "dangerous" haha! but yea got back and talked to masako for a while...and ate ice cream....freshman 15 here i come...lol

so today was fun~~ i had "fantastic" prints in photo workshop~~~ sooo happy that the teacher likes me...and i told the TA that he was scary to me...it was werid that i said that without thinking....i never talk without thinking first..but it just came out...I'M SO MESSED UP~~HA!! but yea for some reason i was sooo HAPPY today! i have no idea why...and i was giggling....I DON'T DO THAT!!! hahaha that was crazy~ my friend was like "wuts wrong with you" and i would just laugh and this is all going on in the darkroom....it was embarrassing but i didn't care~ haha well, made some new friends again today...ppl are soo cool~ haha of course there was one person i wanted to meet and introduce myself to but i felt like an idiot if i did...i hate when that happens tho~ When the a person that looks and seems very interesting is all of the sudden walking by like 50 times a day and you can't talk to them because you feel intimidated....=( soo sad~ well sooner or later i will introduce myself to this guy! hehee

hello~~~~~~~~~~~~~alright today! I'M TIRED!!!connie and matt MADE me go to the galleries on 10th ave!!! and then! went to k-town~~~~ WALKED...my ankles HURT!!! ahhh my ankles are soooo weird...i wish it was saturday...so that i could eat some korean food that my mom made for me!!!! hehehee anyways....i put a poll up on mt info and SOO many people don't want me to get a lip ring! gosh darn it!!! well, i don't know...maybe i shouldn't....but i did wear it around the city today and some ppl llooked at me funny like they were saying..."what is that asian girl doing with a lip ring...." anyways i really don't care~ i might get it...hehee but i kinda want one...oh well...=)

wow it's like 5:35AM...and i'm not tired... interesting....well, i'm in connie's room typing on my laptop that i brought down so that we could listen to music...well, connie's sleeping now cause she has a class at 9 and i don't at all...haha i'm going to be soo tired tomorrow...i'm crazy but it's ok i kinda don't care cause i got all my reading done!! i don't have to read the odyssey! well, there's not much to write...all i can hear is the rain falling and the sound of it hitting the ground is nice and soothing...i love it~ ^.^ it reminds me of MD and how peaceful it was...but yet i don't miss it that much~ it seems like i won't be going to sleep anytime soon so i think i'm going to read the odyssey and probably finish it...the only thing good about being up this late is that i get to talk to xing! he's in cali so it's like 2 AM for him~ yay i get to talk to xing~~~ anyways back to the odyssey~~

isn't weird that your day can be ruined when you hear one sentence that makes you feel terrible and so it RUINS your whole day? or when someone invades your privacy and never realizes that they hurt you when they don't listen? and when something that you hoped for happens but then you don't feel better when you get it...OR even when they listen to you and hear you out but still doesn't get the point? and never gives up to invade your life? maybe even keeps calling and talking but in the end it never making sense....or even when it does you don't want to hear it... especially if it was what you were hoping for....but then you don't want it because you got it after the knowing that you shouldn't trust that person? BECAUSE of one sentence...that means SO MUCH but also SO LITTLE. cuz of what had happened...knowing that there is someone there to hold on to but realizing after that one conversation you're falling through a whole where you were pushed into~ 
i'm falling 
and there will be no one to help me 
because in the mist of falling there is no one else with me. 
i am alone and will forever be in isolation. 
i'll never reach the bottom and i will never see day light. 
there is nothing on this earth that can help me. 
the screams gets louder and the hole gets darker. 
as i fall i wonder about how much of an idiot i am.
there is no way to turn back and i am forever doomed.
i pray and there is no one there.
